data.description: Nice 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch on large 5.9+- acre lot with a POND. Large deck, 1 car attached garage, Heat Pump is approximately a year old, Oil furnace also for back up or additional, screen porch, LARGE barn and  multiple outbuildings!  House has its own well and septic so no water and sewer bills.  Great property and tons of potential!!
